{"title":"播种人","authors":["刘向东"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":4,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘向东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁光闪过，蚯蚓的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着热气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种人的眼里就有了喜气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里就有了底气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有了魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老少爷们儿，精血正壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛他们就是种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子在他们的指纹里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子在他们的脚印里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经生根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论村姑，无论村妇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说自己就是土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和土地一样可靠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让种子呼吸它就呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让日子新鲜它就新鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比新娘还新"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}